						.text-18-author Booke Cagle
					.text-18-content.content
						p Yesterday night, all of a sudden, people shared that article. People from Venice. People who know you. Through them, this morning, I glimpsed a bit of “all the rest”: your art, your energy, your daily life, these people. That art, that music… You seem to be infused with it. And yet, I didn’t see any of it five years ago. Of course I didn’t: there I was, a goddam tourist with her goddam camera.
